OL,4,C1.5m pupils out of school in England
OL,5,Clast week
OL,6, Almost 1.5m pupils were absent from
OL,7, classes in England's primary and
OL,8, secondary schools last week, a snapshot
OL,9, of one day's official data shows.
OL,11,FThe weekly Department for Education
OL,12,Ffigures show about 840,000 were off for
OL,13,FCovid-related reasons and a further
OL,14,F630,000 were absent for other reasons.
OL,16,FIt means a quarter of secondary pupils
OL,17,Fwere out of class on Thursday last
OL,18,Fweek, and 15% of primary pupils.
OL,20,FTeachers' leaders told MPs they were
OL,21,Fhugely concerned about these absences.
